    \\end{array}
  \\right)^n+c_2\\left(
    \\begin{array}{c}
      1 \\\\
      \\frac{1-\\sqrt{5}}{2} \\\\
    \\end{array}
  \\right)^n
\\] where $c_1$ and $c_2$ are constants.

